arts.ttl: Feyenoord leave it late to defeat Fenerbahce
arts.sum: Feyenoord will take a slender lead into the second leg of their Champions League qualifer against Fenerbahce. A 2-1 win was sealed in De Kuip thanks to a 91st minute winner. Before the match it was confirmed that Sem Steijn had replaced Quinten Timber as the new captain of Feyenoord.
